      • explode

        void explode()
        Explodes the transporter and removes it from the steamnet. This should handle any reductions in steamnet steam or pressure. You do not have to actually make an explosion if you don't want to. This is called if shouldExplode() has been called. It must be called during the block/tile entity's update/tick.
